node.text: Every 3 seconds a girl under the age of 18 is married. That’s 12 million girls a year robbed of their futures, put at risk of violence, ill health, and trapped in poverty. Join me in helping to end the international child bride crisis. Head to vowforgirls.org for more info ! @vowforgirls

node.text: March is Women's Month, and I'm so proud to join these strong women ( @sleepinthegardn & @theparisberelc ) and @childrescuecoalition to speak up for children who are being sexually abused across the globe. If you can, please donate to help CRC rescue even more children, and let's turn their whispers into roars. #jointhefight Link in bio 🙏🏼

node.text: Being here with @annebreiter in our favorite place to say our final goodbye to Drew was one of the most tragic and beautiful evenings of my life. Spreading his ashes in a place that he loved so dearly gave us all cathartic release, immense peace, and some final closure towards healing. It won’t ever fully make sense that he’s gone. I miss him more than ever, but sharing stories of him that made us belly laugh and cry just shows how much he is living on through all of us. We love you so much Drew boy ♥️ And I love you more than ever my Annie.

node.text: Happy National Lipstick Day from an indecisive me and @almay! 💄 And guess what? We’re are giving away all 26 shades to you and your friends! To enter, you must follow @almay and tag your friends in their latest Reels video! PS, I ended up choosing Treat Yourself with a hint of Love Yourself ♥️

node.text: dare i say this is my last london photo series ? I’ve begun using words like “lush” “brilliant” “to be fair” regularly, eaten my weight in halloumi cheese, learned the extreme importance of football & have experienced 4 seasons in a day. You could say ive loved it here 💗
